V 1.1+
* DMS
* Roman numerals input
  + lowercase in settings
* SCI/ENG input/output
* other non-standard positional systems (s. WP), e.g. bijective numerals, non-adjacent forms, Egyptian fractions, factorial base, quote notation, …
* alternative positional notation output (0.1 = 0.0'9, balanced ternary: 0.'Z = Z.'1)
* display musical interval name: https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tonstruktur_(mathematische_Beschreibung)
* copy error message to input → base isn’t copied, but id of incriminating char is
* base symbols $%&... customisable
* themes/colours
  + colour of title bar in overview
  + icon adaptive (blue): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ts98gL1JCQU
  + icon shadowed, C in Q

